{"id": 768, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个囤积控你有哪些痛苦？", "description": "活生生过成了一个断舍离的反面。（题图来自：carine brancowitz）", "record_count": 4399, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194432DtuS3p8zLfAHrvYo.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-19T13:07:40Z", "options": [{"id": 45568, "content": "存得越多越认识到自己拖延症已经到了毁了我一生的程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 42755, "content": "一抽屉打火机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423767}, {"id": 74760, "content": "从小到大的课本笔记本参考书资料，全堆在家里落了一层灰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598592}, {"id": 43019, "content": "每次快递的小盒子都留着，觉得万一有个用处，可是现在成了过年清理的垃圾咯??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423630}, {"id": 51219, "content": "纠结图片视频的存储问题", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004802Vfr0U1cECvQi8a9B.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478723}, {"id": 43289, "content": "我妈一直叫我理桌子→_→就不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436471}, {"id": 42778, "content": "我妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417395}, {"id": 43290, "content": "文具控买来都不用→_→你买来干嘛？吃吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436471}, {"id": 46618, "content": "就是屯书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451464}, {"id": 45088, "content": "一套一套的美丽本本", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447144}, {"id": 44321, "content": "各种本子的收藏???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441824}, {"id": 45089, "content": "淘宝收藏夹几次爆满", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447144}, {"id": 43298, "content": "囤积了一堆好不容易得到的优惠券……发现都过期了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403531}, {"id": 43300, "content": "弃之可惜，留之无用～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428735}, {"id": 42791, "content": "买了一堆护肤品，临近快用完的时候又赶紧采购一批，囤着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338568}, {"id": 43815, "content": "把大学所有的教材辅导书练习册及各种杂书都运回了家……果真是对不起房价……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302026}, {"id": 43816, "content": "把大学所有的教材辅导书练习册及各种杂书都运回了家……果真是对不起房价……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302026}, {"id": 42794, "content": "不会收拾！乱！乱！乱！尤其抽屉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423293}, {"id": 45354, "content": "买到没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449560}, {"id": 42540, "content": "普通/水溶/油性彩铅、彩色马克笔、水粉水彩、丙烯、蜡笔……只要是色彩缤纷的能画出东西的都爱买，可是几乎没怎么画……（摊手）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363503}, {"id": 42541, "content": "每次看到喜欢的都要买，但是买了又舍不得用，经常拿出来看看，结果就是一直吃土……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279313}, {"id": 43320, "content": "囤了20斤护肤品…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 47812}, {"id": 45625, "content": "我需要一个更大的家……但我没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414406}, {"id": 42558, "content": "每次理房间只能把东西堆堆齐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268161}, {"id": 54591, "content": "搬家。  丢东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496528}, {"id": 49986, "content": "家里没有地方可以放下我的大拼图", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468734}, {"id": 43332, "content": "巨好看的餐巾纸 卷纸 手帕纸 根本停不下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436596}, {"id": 44357, "content": "塞哪里塞哪里塞哪里？？？啊！崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247838}, {"id": 42313, "content": "去学校或者回家收拾东西前必取舍一番后列清单，然后大包小包上路。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428694}, {"id": 42825, "content": "老被我妈骂", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200852vnCbxqYlHIFMJOX1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433523}, {"id": 51529, "content": "浏 览 器 的 收 藏 夹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480840}, {"id": 42314, "content": "好看的东西都要买双份，一个拿来用，一个拿来囤着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429577}, {"id": 42570, "content": "瓶子啊瓶子，各种矿泉水瓶子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431426}, {"id": 42315, "content": "脂肪囤积很痛苦…", "image": null, "praise_count": 542, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258708}, {"id": 42316, "content": "买的书5辈子都看不完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 438, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358202}, {"id": 42572, "content": "我哭的好奇心日报的设计不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431427}, {"id": 42317, "content": "讨厌的人一辈子都杀不死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358202}, {"id": 42318, "content": "报纸……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426349}, {"id": 42319, "content": "囤伤心 T_T", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135605}, {"id": 42320, "content": "满柜子的护肤品，用到后年都用不完，囤是不对的，可是不囤没有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429860}, {"id": 42577, "content": "拍的照片，不删占空间，删舍不得，但是又不看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431475}, {"id": 46161, "content": "明明家里有一堆本，看到好看的本还是忍不住的买了然后回家就被骂惹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445647}, {"id": 45394, "content": "微信里收藏的一大堆公式总结。尽管知道这辈子大概都不会看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449196}, {"id": 42324, "content": "整个学生时代无数学校发的英语磁带，自己买的正版流行歌磁带、CD唱片、DVD影碟。至今未舍得扔。哎...", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2932}, {"id": 46420, "content": "电影票票根放到褪色……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454536}, {"id": 61524, "content": "积贫积弱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532779}, {"id": 42325, "content": "云盘里一丢丢的电子书，什么时候才能看完", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107787}, {"id": 42326, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219168}, {"id": 42582, "content": "囤积的感情一生也用不完。还有未来吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431540}, {"id": 42327, "content": "看完的视频舍不得删，但其实都不看；设计好看的app舍不得删，但其实都不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 361, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201831}]}